{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":603,"text":"On September 10, the morning\nof my seventh birthday,"},{"time":3928,"text":"I came downstairs to the kitchen,\nwhere my mother was washing the dishes"},{"time":7343,"text":"and my father was reading\nthe paper or something,"},{"time":10000,"text":"and I sort of presented myself to them\nin the doorway, and they said,"},{"time":13310,"text":"\"Hey, happy birthday!\"\nAnd I said, \"I'm seven.\""},{"time":18000,"text":"And my father smiled and said,"},{"time":20000,"text":"\"Well, you know\nwhat that means, don't you?\""},{"time":22410,"text":"And I said, \"Yeah,\nthat I'm going to have a party"},{"time":25260,"text":"and a cake and get a lot of presents?\""},{"time":27507,"text":"And my dad said, \"Well, yes."},{"time":29742,"text":"But more importantly,"},{"time":30926,"text":"being seven means that\nyou've reached the age of reason,"},{"time":33895,"text":"and you're now capable of committing\nany and all sins against God and man.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":38446,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41322,"text":"Now, I had heard this phrase,\n\"age of reason,\" before."},{"time":44572,"text":"Sister Mary Kevin\nhad been bandying it about"},{"time":46847,"text":"my second-grade class at school."},{"time":48568,"text":"But when she said it,"},{"time":49744,"text":"the phrase seemed all caught up\nin the excitement of preparations"},{"time":52829,"text":"for our first communion\nand our first confession,"},{"time":55160,"text":"and everybody knew that was really\nall about the white dress"},{"time":58010,"text":"and the white veil."},{"time":59185,"text":"And anyway, I hadn't really paid\nall that much attention"},{"time":61849,"text":"to that phrase, \"age of reason.\""},{"time":63712,"text":"So, I said, \"Yeah, yeah, age of reason.\nWhat does that mean again?\""},{"time":67924,"text":"And my dad said, \"Well, we believe,\nin the Catholic Church,"},{"time":71578,"text":"that God knows that little kids don't know\nthe difference between right and wrong,"},{"time":75479,"text":"but when you're seven,\nyou're old enough to know better."},{"time":78141,"text":"So, you've grown up\nand reached the age of reason,"},{"time":80780,"text":"and now God will start\nkeeping notes on you,"},{"time":83421,"text":"and begin your permanent record.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":85401,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86435,"text":"And I said, \"Oh ..."},{"time":90767,"text":"Wait a minute."},{"time":92006,"text":"You mean all that time, up till today,"},{"time":95204,"text":"all that time I was so good,\nGod didn't notice it?\""},{"time":99376,"text":"And my mom said, \"Well, I noticed it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":102000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"And I thought, \"How could\nI not have known this before?"},{"time":106609,"text":"How could it not have sunk in\nwhen they'd been telling me?"},{"time":109363,"text":"All that being good\nand no real credit for it."},{"time":111555,"text":"And worst of all,\nhow could I not have realized"},{"time":113788,"text":"this very important information"},{"time":115296,"text":"until the very day\nthat it was basically useless to me?\""},{"time":118242,"text":"So I said, \"Well, Mom and Dad,\nwhat about Santa Claus?"},{"time":121632,"text":"I mean, Santa Claus knows\nif you're naughty or nice, right?\""},{"time":125000,"text":"And my dad said, \"Yeah, but, honey,"},{"time":127000,"text":"I think that's technically just\nbetween Thanksgiving and Christmas.\""},{"time":130289,"text":"And my mother said, \"Oh, Bob, stop it.\nLet's just tell her. I mean, she's seven."},{"time":134725,"text":"Julie, there is no Santa Claus.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":137085,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":140180,"text":"Now, this was actually\nnot that upsetting to me."},{"time":143919,"text":"My parents had this whole\nelaborate story about Santa Claus:"},{"time":146889,"text":"how they had talked to Santa Claus\nhimself and agreed"},{"time":149419,"text":"that instead of Santa\ndelivering our presents"},{"time":151544,"text":"over the night of Christmas Eve,"},{"time":153107,"text":"like he did for every other family\nwho got to open their surprises"},{"time":156246,"text":"first thing Christmas morning,"},{"time":157716,"text":"our family would give Santa more time."},{"time":159707,"text":"Santa would come to our house\nwhile we were at nine o'clock high mass"},{"time":163310,"text":"on Christmas morning, but only\nif all of us kids did not make a fuss."},{"time":167302,"text":"Which made me very suspicious."},{"time":170000,"text":"It was pretty obvious that it was really\nour parents giving us the presents."},{"time":174095,"text":"I mean, my dad had a very\ndistinctive wrapping style,"},{"time":177000,"text":"and my mother's handwriting\nwas so close to Santa's."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179673,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":180855,"text":"Plus, why would Santa save time\nby having to loop back"},{"time":183612,"text":"to our house after he'd gone\nto everybody else's?"},{"time":186740,"text":"There was only one obvious conclusion\nto reach from this mountain of evidence:"},{"time":190534,"text":"our family was too strange and weird\nfor even Santa Claus to come visit,"},{"time":195071,"text":"and my poor parents were trying\nto protect us from the embarrassment,"},{"time":198350,"text":"this humiliation of rejection\nby Santa, who was jolly --"},{"time":202135,"text":"but let's face it,\nhe was also very judgmental."},{"time":205214,"text":"So to find out that there was\nno Santa Claus at all"},{"time":207801,"text":"was actually sort of a relief."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210000,"text":"I left the kitchen not really\nin shock about Santa,"},{"time":212959,"text":"but rather, I was just dumbfounded"},{"time":214684,"text":"about how I could have missed\nthis whole age of reason thing."},{"time":217752,"text":"It was too late for me,\nbut maybe I could help someone else,"},{"time":221000,"text":"someone who could use the information."},{"time":223520,"text":"They had to fit two criteria:"},{"time":225197,"text":"they had to be old enough\nto be able to understand"},{"time":227562,"text":"the whole concept of the age\nof reason, and not yet seven."},{"time":231125,"text":"The answer was clear:\nmy brother Bill. He was six."},{"time":234277,"text":"Well, I finally found Bill"},{"time":235563,"text":"about a block away from our house\nat this public school playground."},{"time":238796,"text":"It was a Saturday,\nand he was all by himself,"},{"time":240936,"text":"just kicking a ball\nagainst the side of a wall."},{"time":243166,"text":"I ran up to him and said, \"Bill!"},{"time":245000,"text":"I just realized that the age of reason\nstarts when you turn seven,"},{"time":248167,"text":"and then you're capable\nof committing any and all sins"},{"time":250737,"text":"against God and man.\""},{"time":251912,"text":"And Bill said, \"So?\""},{"time":253924,"text":"And I said, \"So, you're six."},{"time":255934,"text":"You have a whole year to do anything\nyou want to and God won't notice it.\""},{"time":259996,"text":"And he said, \"So?\""},{"time":261762,"text":"And I said, \"So? So everything!\""},{"time":265357,"text":"And I turned to run.\nI was so angry with him."},{"time":268206,"text":"But when I got to the top of the steps,"},{"time":270104,"text":"I turned around dramatically and said,"},{"time":271945,"text":"\"Oh, by the way, Bill --\nthere is no Santa Claus.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":275400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":277352,"text":"Now, I didn't know it at the time,"},{"time":279115,"text":"but I really wasn't turning seven\non September 10th."},{"time":282285,"text":"For my 13th birthday,"},{"time":283634,"text":"I planned a slumber party\nwith all of my girlfriends,"},{"time":286229,"text":"but a couple of weeks beforehand\nmy mother took me aside and said,"},{"time":289855,"text":"\"I need to speak to you privately."},{"time":293101,"text":"September 10th is not your birthday.\nIt's October 10th.\""},{"time":297106,"text":"And I said, \"What?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":298679,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":299718,"text":"And she said ..."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301003,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":302581,"text":"\"Listen. The cut-off date to start\nkindergarten was September 15th.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":308000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":309227,"text":"\"So I told them that your birthday\nwas September 10th,"},{"time":312068,"text":"and then I wasn't sure"},{"time":313243,"text":"that you weren't just going to go\nblab it all over the place,"},{"time":316135,"text":"so I started to tell you\nyour birthday was September 10th."},{"time":319841,"text":"But, Julie, you were so ready to start\nschool, honey. You were so ready.\""},{"time":324070,"text":"I thought about it, and when I was four,"},{"time":326000,"text":"I was already the oldest of four children,"},{"time":328024,"text":"and my mother even had\nanother child to come,"},{"time":330167,"text":"so what I think she --\nunderstandably -- really meant"},{"time":332696,"text":"was that she was so ready,\nshe was so ready."},{"time":335095,"text":"Then she said, \"Don't worry, Julie."},{"time":336793,"text":"Every year on October 10th,"},{"time":338286,"text":"when it was your birthday\nbut you didn't realize it,"},{"time":341160,"text":"I made sure that you ate\na piece of cake that day.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":344401,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347252,"text":"Which was comforting, but troubling."},{"time":349570,"text":"My mother had been celebrating\nmy birthday with me, without me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353133,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":354165,"text":"What was so upsetting\nabout this new piece of information"},{"time":357178,"text":"was not that I had to change\nthe date of my slumber party"},{"time":359877,"text":"with all of my girlfriends."},{"time":361203,"text":"What was most upsetting\nwas that this meant I was not a Virgo."},{"time":365087,"text":"I had a huge Virgo poster in my bedroom."},{"time":368186,"text":"And I read my horoscope every single day,"},{"time":370783,"text":"and it was so totally me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":375000,"text":"And this meant that I was a Libra?"},{"time":377753,"text":"So, I took the bus downtown\nto get the new Libra poster."},{"time":381091,"text":"The Virgo poster is a picture\nof a beautiful woman with long hair,"},{"time":384512,"text":"sort of lounging by some water,"},{"time":386068,"text":"but the Libra poster is just a huge scale."},{"time":388926,"text":"This was around the time\nthat I started filling out physically,"},{"time":391917,"text":"and I was filling out a lot more\nthan a lot of the other girls,"},{"time":394924,"text":"and frankly, the whole idea\nthat my astrological sign was a scale"},{"time":398652,"text":"just seemed ominous and depressing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":404169,"text":"But I got the new Libra poster,"},{"time":406000,"text":"and I started to read\nmy new Libra horoscope,"},{"time":409301,"text":"and I was astonished to find\nthat it was also totally me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413751,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":415311,"text":"It wasn't until years later, looking back"},{"time":417316,"text":"on this whole age-of-reason,\nchange-of-birthday thing,"},{"time":419999,"text":"that it dawned on me:"},{"time":421310,"text":"I wasn't turning seven\nwhen I thought I turned seven."},{"time":423857,"text":"I had a whole other month"},{"time":425127,"text":"to do anything I wanted to\nbefore God started keeping tabs on me."},{"time":429238,"text":"Oh, life can be so cruel."},{"time":433317,"text":"One day, two Mormon\nmissionaries came to my door."},{"time":437192,"text":"Now, I just live off a main\nthoroughfare in Los Angeles,"},{"time":439852,"text":"and my block is -- well,\nit's a natural beginning"},{"time":442175,"text":"for people who are peddling\nthings door to door."},{"time":444588,"text":"Sometimes I get little old ladies\nfrom the Seventh Day Adventist Church"},{"time":448000,"text":"showing me these cartoon\npictures of heaven."},{"time":450186,"text":"And sometimes I get\nteenagers who promise me"},{"time":452450,"text":"that they won't join a gang\nand just start robbing people,"},{"time":455329,"text":"if I only buy some\nmagazine subscriptions from them."},{"time":458556,"text":"So normally, I just ignore the doorbell,\nbut on this day, I answered."},{"time":463000,"text":"And there stood two boys, each about 19,\nin white, starched short-sleeved shirts,"},{"time":468309,"text":"and they had little name tags"},{"time":469793,"text":"that identified them\nas official representatives"},{"time":472110,"text":"of the Church of Jesus Christ\nof Latter-day Saints,"},{"time":474935,"text":"and they said they had\na message for me, from God."},{"time":478629,"text":"I said, \"A message for me? From God?\"\nAnd they said, \"Yes.\""},{"time":483848,"text":"Now, I was raised\nin the Pacific Northwest,"},{"time":486000,"text":"around a lot of Church of Latter-day\nSaints people and, you know,"},{"time":489111,"text":"I've worked with them and even dated them,"},{"time":491144,"text":"but I never really knew the doctrine,"},{"time":492946,"text":"or what they said to people\nwhen they were out on a mission,"},{"time":495782,"text":"and I guess I was sort of curious,\nso I said, \"Well, please, come in.\""},{"time":499111,"text":"And they looked really happy,"},{"time":500532,"text":"because I don't think this happens\nto them all that often."}]},{"cues":[{"time":503286,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":504317,"text":"And I sat them down,\nand I got them glasses of water --"},{"time":518085,"text":"Ok, I got it, I got it."},{"time":519664,"text":"I got them glasses of water."},{"time":521093,"text":"Don't touch my hair, that's the thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522943,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":525952,"text":"You can't put a video\nof myself in front of me"},{"time":529000,"text":"and expect me not to fix my hair."},{"time":530938,"text":"Ok."}]},{"cues":[{"time":532290,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":536401,"text":"So I sat them down\nand I got them glasses of water,"},{"time":538816,"text":"and after niceties, they said,"},{"time":540797,"text":"\"Do you believe that God loves you\nwith all his heart?\""},{"time":543433,"text":"And I thought, \"Well,\nof course I believe in God,"},{"time":547000,"text":"but you know, I don't like\nthat word 'heart,'"},{"time":549535,"text":"because it anthropomorphizes God,"},{"time":552000,"text":"and I don't like the word, 'his,'\neither, because that sexualizes God.\""},{"time":556677,"text":"But I didn't want to argue\nsemantics with these boys,"},{"time":559198,"text":"so after a very long,\nuncomfortable pause, I said,"},{"time":562903,"text":"\"Yes, yes, I do. I feel very loved.\""},{"time":566862,"text":"And they looked at each other and smiled,"},{"time":568862,"text":"like that was the right answer."},{"time":570957,"text":"And then they said, \"Do you believe"},{"time":572664,"text":"that we're all brothers\nand sisters on this planet?\""},{"time":575135,"text":"And I said, \"Yes, I do.\""},{"time":576310,"text":"And I was so relieved that it was\na question I could answer so quickly."},{"time":579686,"text":"And they said, \"Well, then\nwe have a story to tell you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":582801,"text":"And they told me this story\nall about this guy named Lehi,"},{"time":586000,"text":"who lived in Jerusalem in 600 BC."},{"time":588907,"text":"Now, apparently in Jerusalem in 600 BC,\neveryone was completely bad and evil."},{"time":593480,"text":"Every single one of them:\nman, woman, child, infant, fetus."},{"time":597000,"text":"And God came to Lehi and said to him,"},{"time":599660,"text":"\"Put your family on a boat\nand I will lead you out of here.\""},{"time":602569,"text":"And God did lead them."},{"time":604000,"text":"He led them to America."},{"time":607172,"text":"I said, \"America?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":608667,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":610756,"text":"From Jerusalem to America\nby boat in 600 BC?\""},{"time":615443,"text":"And they said, \"Yes.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":617000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":618879,"text":"Then they told me\nhow Lehi and his descendants"},{"time":621167,"text":"reproduced and reproduced,\nand over the course of 600 years,"},{"time":624066,"text":"there were two great races of them,\nthe Nephites and the Lamanites,"},{"time":627344,"text":"and the Nephites were totally good --\neach and every one of them --"},{"time":630818,"text":"and the Lamanites\nwere totally bad and evil --"},{"time":633009,"text":"every single one of them\njust bad to the bone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635184,"text":"Then, after Jesus died\non the cross for our sins,"},{"time":638716,"text":"on his way up to heaven,"},{"time":639907,"text":"he stopped by America\nand visited the Nephites."}]},{"cues":[{"time":642504,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":643554,"text":"And he told them that if they all remained\ntotally, totally good --"},{"time":647066,"text":"each and every one of them --"},{"time":648472,"text":"they would win the war\nagainst the evil Lamanites."},{"time":651197,"text":"But apparently somebody blew it,"},{"time":653722,"text":"because the Lamanites\nwere able to kill all the Nephites."},{"time":656483,"text":"All but one guy, this guy named Mormon,"},{"time":658773,"text":"who managed to survive\nby hiding in the woods."},{"time":661543,"text":"And he made sure\nthis whole story was written down"},{"time":664277,"text":"in reformed Egyptian hieroglyphics\nchiseled onto gold plates,"},{"time":668669,"text":"which he then buried\nnear Palmyra, New York."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":677259,"text":"Well, I was just on the edge of my seat."}]},{"cues":[{"time":680000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":683366,"text":"I said, \"What happened to the Lamanites?\""},{"time":686242,"text":"And they said, \"Well, they became\nour Native Americans, here in the U.S.\""},{"time":690108,"text":"And I said, \"So, you believe\nthe Native Americans are descended"},{"time":693318,"text":"from a people who were totally evil?\""},{"time":695383,"text":"And they said, \"Yes.\""},{"time":697627,"text":"Then they told me\nhow this guy named Joseph Smith"},{"time":700707,"text":"found those buried gold plates\nright in his backyard,"},{"time":704366,"text":"and he also found this magic stone\nback there that he put into his hat"},{"time":708112,"text":"and then buried his face into,"},{"time":709634,"text":"and this allowed him\nto translate the gold plates"},{"time":712018,"text":"from the reformed Egyptian into English."}]},{"cues":[{"time":714890,"text":"Well, at this point I just wanted to give\nthese two boys some advice"},{"time":718289,"text":"about their pitch."}]},{"cues":[{"time":719742,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":722607,"text":"I wanted to say --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":723791,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":725481,"text":"\"Ok, don't start with this story.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":727771,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":729000,"text":"I mean, even the Scientologists"},{"time":731067,"text":"know to start with a personality test\nbefore they start --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":734376,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":736000,"text":"telling people all about Xenu,\nthe evil intergalactic overlord."},{"time":741138,"text":"Then, they said, \"Do you believe\nthat God speaks to us"},{"time":743749,"text":"through his righteous prophets?\""},{"time":745313,"text":"And I said, \"No, I don't,\""},{"time":746590,"text":"because I was sort of upset\nabout this Lamanite story"},{"time":749099,"text":"and this crazy gold plate story,"},{"time":750675,"text":"but the truth was,\nI hadn't really thought this through,"},{"time":753533,"text":"so I backpedaled a little and I said,"},{"time":755755,"text":"\"Well, what exactly\ndo you mean by 'righteous'?"},{"time":758666,"text":"And what do you mean by prophets?\nLike, could the prophets be women?\""},{"time":762150,"text":"And they said, \"No.\" And I said, \"Why?\""},{"time":765720,"text":"And they said, \"Well, it's because\nGod gave women a gift"},{"time":769463,"text":"that is so spectacular,"},{"time":771458,"text":"it is so wonderful, that the only gift\nhe had left over to give men"},{"time":776259,"text":"was the gift of prophecy.\""},{"time":778656,"text":"What is this wonderful gift\nGod gave women, I wondered?"},{"time":782003,"text":"Maybe their greater ability\nto cooperate and adapt?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":785366,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":786402,"text":"Women's longer lifespan?"},{"time":787803,"text":"The fact that women tend to be\nmuch less violent than men?"},{"time":791031,"text":"But no -- it wasn't any of these gifts."},{"time":793313,"text":"They said, \"Well, it's her ability\nto bear children.\""},{"time":796401,"text":"I said, \"Oh, come on."},{"time":797853,"text":"I mean, even if women\ntried to have a baby every single year"},{"time":800696,"text":"from the time they were 15\nto the time they were 45,"},{"time":803657,"text":"assuming they didn't die from exhaustion,"},{"time":805677,"text":"it still seems like some women\nwould have some time left over"},{"time":808589,"text":"to hear the word of God.\""},{"time":810059,"text":"And they said, \"No.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":812000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":815000,"text":"Well, then they didn't look so\nfresh-faced and cute to me any more,"},{"time":818188,"text":"but they had more to say."},{"time":819417,"text":"They said, \"Well, we also believe\nthat if you're a Mormon,"},{"time":822175,"text":"and if you're in good standing\nwith the church,"},{"time":824413,"text":"when you die, you get to go to heaven"},{"time":826573,"text":"and be with your family for all eternity.\""},{"time":829378,"text":"And I said, \"Oh, dear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":831460,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":838388,"text":"That wouldn't be\nsuch a good incentive for me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":840611,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":841935,"text":"And they said, \"Oh."}]},{"cues":[{"time":843444,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":844827,"text":"Hey! Well, we also believe\nthat when you go to heaven,"},{"time":847896,"text":"you get your body restored to you\nin its best original state."},{"time":850807,"text":"Like, if you'd lost a leg,\nwell, you get it back."},{"time":853261,"text":"Or, if you'd gone blind, you could see.\""},{"time":855261,"text":"I said, \"Oh. Now, I don't have a uterus,"},{"time":858254,"text":"because I had cancer a few years ago."},{"time":860369,"text":"So does this mean\nthat if I went to heaven,"},{"time":862439,"text":"I would get my old uterus back?\""},{"time":864495,"text":"And they said, \"Sure.\""},{"time":866575,"text":"And I said, \"I don't want it back.\nI'm happy without it.\" Gosh."},{"time":872364,"text":"What if you had a nose job\nand you liked it?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":875355,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":877085,"text":"Would God force you\nto get your old nose back?"},{"time":880824,"text":"Then they gave me this Book of Mormon,"},{"time":882769,"text":"told me to read\nthis chapter and that chapter,"},{"time":884946,"text":"and said they'd come back\nand check in on me,"},{"time":887248,"text":"and I think I said something\nlike, \"Please don't hurry,\""},{"time":889937,"text":"or maybe just, \"Please don't,\"\nand they were gone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":892339,"text":"Ok, so I initially felt\nreally superior to these boys,"},{"time":894951,"text":"and smug in my more conventional faith."},{"time":898417,"text":"But then the more I thought about it,\nthe more I had to be honest with myself."},{"time":902120,"text":"If someone came to my door"},{"time":903447,"text":"and I was hearing Catholic theology\nand dogma for the very first time,"},{"time":906816,"text":"and they said, \"We believe that God\nimpregnated a very young girl"},{"time":910414,"text":"without the use of intercourse,"},{"time":912000,"text":"and the fact that she was a virgin\nis maniacally important to us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":915215,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":916541,"text":"\"And she had a baby,\nand that's the son of God,\""},{"time":919712,"text":"I mean, I would think\nthat's equally ridiculous."},{"time":922000,"text":"I'm just so used to that story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":923886,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":925000,"text":"So, I couldn't let myself feel\ncondescending towards these boys."},{"time":928480,"text":"But the question they asked me\nwhen they first arrived"},{"time":931064,"text":"really stuck in my head:"},{"time":932548,"text":"Did I believe that God\nloved me with all his heart?"},{"time":936000,"text":"Because I wasn't exactly sure\nhow I felt about that question."},{"time":939542,"text":"Now, if they had asked me,"},{"time":940841,"text":"\"Do you feel that God loves\nyou with all his heart?\""},{"time":944091,"text":"Well, that would have been much different,\nI think I would have instantly answered,"},{"time":948121,"text":"\"Yes, yes, I feel it all the time."},{"time":949770,"text":"I feel God's love\nwhen I'm hurt and confused,"},{"time":952539,"text":"and I feel consoled and cared for."},{"time":955191,"text":"I take shelter in God's love when\nI don't understand why tragedy hits,"},{"time":959283,"text":"and I feel God's love when I look\nwith gratitude at all the beauty I see.\""},{"time":963548,"text":"But since they asked me that question\nwith the word \"believe\" in it,"},{"time":966774,"text":"somehow it was all different,"},{"time":968256,"text":"because I wasn't exactly sure\nif I believed what I so clearly felt."}]}]}